    <h2 id="ï¸-project-of-the-day-secure-api-gateway-policy-design">ğŸ› ï¸ Project of the Day: â€œSecure API Gateway Policy Designâ€</h2>
    <p><strong>Scenario:</strong><br />
Youâ€™re tasked with designing a gateway policy for all backend APIs exposed to external partners.
<strong>Steps:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Define 3 API endpoints (e.g., <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/users</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/orders</code>, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">/status</code>)</li>
